    "description": "Welcome to Rainbowcore Hypernova, the explosively fun and absurd fighting game experience!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose from seven vibrant and colorful characters, each representing a different color of the rainbow.<br></li><li>Master the easy-to-learn controls with just three buttons and a variety of motion inputs.<br></li><li>Engage in fast-paced and dynamic battles with a unique arsenal of moves for every character.<br></li><li>Immerse yourself in a banger soundtrack that blends epic music with absurd mouth noises.<br></li><li>Explosive visuals set against the backdrop of a surreal underground mushroom cave.<br></li><li>Connect with other players seamlessly through peer-to-peer rollback netcode gameplay.<br></li><li>Best of all, Rainbowcore Hypernova is completely free to play!</li></ul><br>Join the Rainbowcore Hypernova community and unleash your inner fighter. Show off your skills and become the ultimate Rainbowcore Hypernova champion!<br><br>Epilepsy warning: This game contains many flashing images and animations",
